00:29:10,584 --> 00:29:12,251
不是 我的主意是系统验证模式
No, SCIF mode was my idea.

702
00:29:12,319 --> 00:29:13,964
那你为什么看着我放在桌上的枪
Then why did you look at my gun on the table?

703
00:29:13,988 --> 00:29:15,320
我没看你的枪
I wasn't looking at your gun.

704
00:29:15,389 --> 00:29:17,422
Vance主任
Director Vance,

