美国国防部长吗
the United States Secretary of Defense?

707
00:29:23,864 --> 00:29:26,431
我当然不希望是这样的
I certainly hope not.

708
00:29:36,353 --> 00:29:39,888
你挟持我每多20分钟
I figure every 20 minutes you hold me hostage,

709
00:29:39,956 --> 00:29:41,823
你的徒刑就会增加一年
there's another year on your sentence.

710
00:29:41,892 --> 00:29:44,893
是吗 等等 挟持
Huh? Wait, what? Hostage?

711
00:29:44,961 --> 00:29:45,908
那就是你做的事 不是吗
Well, that's what you're doing, isn't it?

712
00:29:45,932 --> 00:29:46,795
不不不
No. No, no, no.

713
00:29:46,796 --> 00:29:47,962
不是
Not at all.

714
00:29:48,031 --> 00:29:50,899
系统验证模式切断了手机信号
Well, SCIF mode cuts cell service...

715
00:29:50,967 --> 00:29:51,900
而你又装备了武器
and you're armed.

716
00:29:51,968 --> 00:29:54,135
哦 这个啊
Oh-- Oh, this?

717
00:29:54,204 --> 00:29:56,237
哦不 这个 还是个皮套子
Oh, no, this is, uh, it's still holstered.

718
00:29:56,306 --> 00:29:58,373
我们只是要求多点时间 长官
Yeah, we-we're merely asking for more time, sir.

719
00:29:58,441 --> 00:30:01,342
你们的嫌犯不会再说什么了 他已经明确了
Your suspect isn't gonna talk. He's made that quite clear.

720
00:30:01,411 --> 00:30:04,345
我告诉过你们 我不需要医疗救助
I told you, I don't want any medical help.

721
00:30:09,152 --> 00:30:11,719
嘿
Hey!

722
00:30:11,788 --> 00:30:13,354
我要打电话
I want my phone call!

723
00:30:15,258 --> 00:30:19,027
我 我 想和我妈妈说话
I... I-- geez, I want to talk to my mom.

724
00:30:19,095 --> 00:30:21,863
安全锁定 继续锁定
Security lockdown on... Going on lockdown.

725
00:30:21,932 --> 00:30:25,400
第一批应急人员已到现场
We got first responders on the ground...

726
00:30:34,578 --> 00:30:35,710
不行
No.

727
00:30:35,779 --> 00:30:37,512
Bishop不行 停下
Bishop, no. Stop, stop.

728
00:30:37,581 --> 00:30:40,281
呆在那里 不行
You stay there. No!

729
00:30:40,350 --> 00:30:42,183
继续告诉我消息
Y-You keep me informed.

730
00:30:44,654 --> 00:30:46,788
发生什么了
Hey. What's-what's going on?

731
00:30:46,856 --> 00:30:48,790
出什么事了
Is something wrong?

732
00:30:51,795 --> 00:30:53,728
当局赶到现场
Authorities are just arriving on the scene.

733
00:30:53,797 --> 00:30:56,764
拆弹组和危险品处理小组已经进入大楼
Metro bomb squad and Hazmat teams have entered the building.

734
00:30:56,833 --> 00:31:00,234
联邦当局刚发布了官方声明
While federal authorities have yet to issue a formal statement,

735
00:31:00,303 --> 00:31:03,071
警方要求特区地区的市民
police are asking everyone in the greater D.C. area

736
00:31:03,139 --> 00:31:04,939
呆在家中
to remain in their homes.

737
00:31:05,008 --> 00:31:07,442
你的气体被用在了袭击事件中
Your gas was used in an attack.

738
00:31:07,510 --> 00:31:10,645
这是WJGZ节目先前收到的
Again, here is the footage WJGZ received earlier,

739
00:31:10,714 --> 00:31:12,280
用手机拍摄的视频
taken with a cell phone.

740
00:31:12,349 --> 00:31:15,116
这段视频年龄较小的观众不宜观看
This video may not be suitable for younger viewers.

741
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:32,266
快走 快走 快走
Go, go, go!

742
00:31:32,335 --> 00:31:35,236
不 这说不通
No. This doesn't make any sense.

743
00:31:35,305 --> 00:31:37,572
-当然说不通 -这是恐怖袭击
- Of course it doesn't. - It's terrorism!

744
00:31:37,641 --> 00:31:38,851
这说明你的上个行动
Which means your last act on Earth

745
00:31:38,875 --> 00:31:40,219
会杀死无辜民众
will be the killing of innocent people.

746
00:31:40,243 --> 00:31:41,843
那和你的基石相符吗
Think that'll fit on your headstone?

747
00:31:41,911 --> 00:31:44,278
-我是信的 -不不 那不是
- I'll make sure it does. - No, no. That's not...

748
00:31:44,347 --> 00:31:45,371
那不是我
That's-that's not what I...

749
00:31:45,395 --> 00:31:47,395
那你再找出个人来让我们责备
Well, then, you give me someone else to blame!

750
00:31:47,417 --> 00:31:51,185
我把箱子给了一个海关探员
Uh, okay, uh, I-I gave the crate to a customs agent.

751
00:31:51,254 --> 00:31:52,920
地址
Address.

752
00:31:52,989 --> 00:31:55,323
他不知道里面有什么
Uh, he didn't know what was inside.

753
00:31:55,392 --> 00:31:56,824
他一定打开过
He must have opened it.

754
00:32:01,498 --> 00:32:02,930
Leon 那是我想的那样吧
Leon, is this what I think it is?

755
00:32:11,408 --> 00:32:13,374
我要完蛋了
I'll be damned.

756
00:32:17,013 --> 00:32:18,893
-我已获知... -闭路电视5频道
-I'm now being told... - Closed circuit, channel five.

757
00:32:18,948 --> 00:32:20,860
酒店已经被疏散 紧急救援部门
the hotel has been evacuated, and that emergency services

758
00:32:20,884 --> 00:32:23,551
正继续在该地展开...
are continuing to fan out throughout the area...

759
00:32:23,620 --> 00:32:26,187
嘿 呃 谢谢你 Ross先生
Hey, uh, thank you. Thank you, Mr. Ross,

760
00:32:26,256 --> 00:32:27,522
不过你可以不用读了
but you can stop reading now.

761
00:32:32,862 --> 00:32:37,331
呃 稿子到这里结束了 所以我即兴创作了最后一段
The, uh, script ended, so I improvised that last part.

762
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:39,111
-我希望没啥问题 -Bishop探员给我发了消息
- I hope that was okay. - Agent Bishop texted me.

763
00:32:39,135 --> 00:32:40,334
你简直棒极了
You were perfect.

764
00:32:40,403 --> 00:32:43,971
部长 主任
Mr. Secretary, Mr. Director.

765
00:32:44,040 --> 00:32:45,373
非常感谢你允许我
Thank you so much for allowing me

766
00:32:45,442 --> 00:32:46,886
成为你们军事演习的一部分
to be a part of your operations drill.

767
00:32:46,910 --> 00:32:50,311
我 我得说 这对我来说是个全新的任务
I, uh, have to say, this was a new one for me.

768
00:32:50,380 --> 00:32:52,013
是啊 对我们来说也是
Yeah. Us, too.

769
00:32:52,082 --> 00:32:54,048
Hines小姐 这个广播节目
Miss Hines, this broadcast

770
00:32:54,117 --> 00:32:56,818
只通过闭路电视播出了 对吗
was only sent via closed circuit, right?

771
00:32:56,886 --> 00:32:59,187
-是的 只在我们大楼里 主任 -那些镜头
- Yes. Our building only, Director. - The footage,

772
00:32:59,255 --> 00:33:01,489
-到处逃跑的人们 -呃那些研讨会上的
- the running people. - Uh, the agents

773
00:33:01,558 --> 00:33:03,891
探员们愿意提供帮助
at the seminar, they were happy to help.

774
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:07,261
我们告诉他们这是一个 执法舆情学 的演练
We told them it was an exercise in "Optics In Law Enforcement."

775
00:33:07,330 --> 00:33:09,163
尸体都是真的尸体
And the bodies were the cadavers.

776
00:33:09,232 --> 00:33:10,865
并不是那样 长官
Not exactly, sir,

777
00:33:10,934 --> 00:33:13,668
不过我喜欢你那么想
but I like where your head is at.

778
00:33:14,804 --> 00:33:17,371
我很抱歉 部长先生
I'm so sorry, uh, Mr. Secretary.

779
00:33:19,609 --> 00:33:21,075
该死的Gibss哪儿去了
Where the hell is Gibbs?

780
00:33:27,083 --> 00:33:28,783
联邦探员
Federal agents.

781
00:33:28,852 --> 00:33:30,852
嘿 举起手来
Hey, put your hands in the air.

782
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:32,220
离那个集装箱远一点
Back away from the container.

783
00:33:55,712 --> 00:33:57,879
啊 没啥问题
Oh, looks good.

784
00:34:00,683 --> 00:34:03,050
警报解除 没有泄露
All clear, six-eight.

785
00:34:10,660 --> 00:34:13,828
哇哦 这些很老旧了吧
Wow. These are old, huh?

786
00:34:13,897 --> 00:34:17,365
他们为什么不销毁呢
Why weren't they destroyed?

787
00:34:17,433 --> 00:34:20,668
回收那些毒气并不能开脱NCIS的责任
Recovering that gas does not absolve NCIS.

788
00:34:20,737 --> 00:34:22,937
除了不遵从命令 非法黑客行为
In addition to disobeying orders, illegal hacking

789
00:34:23,006 --> 00:34:25,306
以及威胁政府要员 你还可以加上..
and-and threatening a government official, you can add...

790
00:34:25,375 --> 00:34:27,575
见鬼了 我甚至还不知道该怎么称呼这个局面
well, hell, I don't even know what to call this charade.

791
00:34:27,644 --> 00:34:29,443
这不是胁迫 也不是诱捕
It's not coercion and it's not entrapment.

792
00:34:29,512 --> 00:34:31,913
-没什么用 McGee探员 -我全怪你 Leon
- Not helping, Agent McGee. - And I blame you, Leon.

793
00:34:31,981 --> 00:34:34,615
你就是这样运作你部门的吗 还有那个该死的Gibbs哪儿去了
Is this how you run your house? And where the hell is Gibbs?

794
00:34:34,684 --> 00:34:36,918
在这儿
Right here.

795
00:34:36,986 --> 00:34:38,946
Gibbs 你的警徽也可以丢进这堆了
Gibbs, you can add your badge to the growing pile.

796
00:34:43,860 --> 00:34:46,260
这也给你了
You should have this, too.

797
00:34:46,329 --> 00:34:47,862
那是什么
And what's that?

798
00:34:47,931 --> 00:34:51,666
Trine化工说他们按照军事合同的要求
Trine Chemical said they destroyed all their chlorine,

799
00:34:51,734 --> 00:34:52,834
销毁了全部氯气
per military contracts.

800
00:34:52,902 --> 00:34:54,502
但那都是鬼扯
Well, that's total BS.

801
00:34:54,571 --> 00:34:57,138
是啊 为了省钱他们撒谎了 实际上省了几百万
Yeah, they lied to save a buck. Millions, actually.

802
00:34:57,207 --> 00:34:58,539
我们调查了他们的记录
We went through their records.

803
00:34:58,608 --> 00:34:59,674
你们是非法调查
Illegally obtained.

804
00:34:59,742 --> 00:35:01,042
不 我们有搜查令
No, pretty sure we had a warrant.

805
00:35:01,110 --> 00:35:02,476
当这一切结束时
When this is all over,

806
00:35:02,545 --> 00:35:04,645
-他们公司的股票就会崩溃 -就让他们崩溃啊
- company stock will crash. - Let it.

807
00:35:04,714 --> 00:35:07,481
他们欺骗了美国政府 你想说什么
They defrauded the United States government. Your point?

808
00:35:07,550 --> 00:35:09,617
我想说 长官 你是他们的重要股东
My point, sir, is that you are a major shareholder,

809
00:35:09,686 --> 00:35:11,096
而且你将会损失大量财富
and you stand to lose a lot of money.

810
00:35:11,120 --> 00:35:12,987
你认为我介入是钱的原因
You think I stepped in because of money?

811
00:35:13,056 --> 00:35:15,022
或者是因为你与CEO的友谊
Or your friendship with the CEO.

812
00:35:15,091 --> 00:35:18,025
我从未想到...
I-It never occurred to me that...

813
00:35:18,094 --> 00:35:21,362
在州政府要求我介入时 我不知道Trine卷入其中
I had no idea Trine was involved when State asked me to step in.

814
00:35:21,431 --> 00:35:22,797
放松 我们知道
Relax. We know.

815
00:35:22,866 --> 00:35:24,999
我和George Green好几个月没聊过了
And I haven't talked to George Green in months.

816
00:35:25,068 --> 00:35:26,412
至少这几天确实没有 我们查过了
Certainly not in the last few days. We checked.

817
00:35:26,436 --> 00:35:29,570
天啊 这看起来真糟糕
Geez, this looks bad.

818
00:35:29,639 --> 00:35:31,772
但这并不意味着存在犯罪行为
Doesn't always mean there was a crime.

819
00:35:31,841 --> 00:35:33,407
对吗 主任
Right, Director?

820
00:35:36,446 --> 00:35:39,480
我想NCIS不是唯一一个
I guess NCIS weren't the only ones

821
00:35:39,549 --> 00:35:40,882
抢跑的人
who jumped the gun a little.

822
00:35:40,950 --> 00:35:42,183
在简报
Outside of briefings,

823
00:35:42,252 --> 00:35:43,652
以及偶尔的社交聚会之外
and the occasional social gathering,

824
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:45,219
我和你互不相识 Leon
you and I don't know each other, Leon.

825
00:35:45,288 --> 00:35:47,655
我做了最坏的打算
I assumed the worst.

826
00:35:47,724 --> 00:35:49,857
我们都会犯错
Well, we all make mistakes.

827
00:35:49,926 --> 00:35:52,037
是啊 就像Bibbs探员和他的团队刚才提醒我的
Yes, as Agent Gibbs and his team have just reminded me.

828
00:35:52,061 --> 00:35:53,661
好吧 如果是这样的话 主任
Well, if that's it, Director,

829
00:35:53,730 --> 00:35:56,097
我要去参加一个新闻发布会
I got a press conference to attend.

830
00:35:56,165 --> 00:35:56,885
长官
Sir?

831
00:35:56,909 --> 00:35:57,833
我得走在前面
I have to get in front of this.

832
00:35:57,834 --> 00:36:02,737
为我的失误负起责任 还要祝贺NCIS完成了他们的任务
Take responsibility for my part, and congratulate NCIS on theirs.

833
00:36:02,805 --> 00:36:04,906
也许下一次
Maybe next time,

834
00:36:04,974 --> 00:36:08,542
我们都会更加谨慎 对吗
we could both be a little more careful. Yeah?

835
00:36:19,255 --> 00:36:21,289
不对
Nope.

836
00:36:21,357 --> 00:36:22,423
干得好
Well done.

837
00:36:22,492 --> 00:36:24,625
-这是你的 -谢谢
- This is yours. - Oh. Thank you.

838
00:36:24,694 --> 00:36:26,438
在这场新闻发布会上
In a news conference addressing this discovery,

839
00:36:26,462 --> 00:36:28,763
美国国防部长Wynn Crawford
United States Secretary of Defense Wynn Crawford

840
00:36:28,831 --> 00:36:30,865
声称对Trine化工的指控
noted that the allegations against Trine Chemical

841
00:36:30,934 --> 00:36:32,566
是一个孤立事件
are an isolated event.

842
00:36:32,635 --> 00:36:35,536
哇哦 一个政客愿意承认他错了
Wow, a politician willing to admit that he was wrong.

843
00:36:35,605 --> 00:36:37,182
-太新奇了 -我知道一切
- It's refreshing. - I knew everything

844
00:36:37,206 --> 00:36:38,906
都会好起来
was gonna be fine.

845
00:36:38,975 --> 00:36:41,108
我一秒都没有怀疑过Gibbs
I never doubted Gibbs one second.

846
00:36:41,177 --> 00:36:42,944
我怀疑了 不过我在适应
I did. But I'm learning.

847
00:36:47,517 --> 00:36:49,583
嘿 Ellie
Hey, Ellie?

848
00:36:49,652 --> 00:36:50,652
嗯
Hmm?

849
00:36:51,976 --> 00:36:53,561
有时间吗
You have a sec?

850
00:36:53,562 --> 00:36:55,195
有 怎么了
Yeah. What's up?

851
00:36:58,200 --> 00:37:01,134
我是想对你的约会道个歉
I just wanted to apologize about your date.

852
00:37:01,203 --> 00:37:04,004
下一次你和Boyd共进晚餐
Next time that Boyd and you go out to dinner,

853
00:37:04,073 --> 00:37:05,505
呃 我来付账
uh, it'll be on me.

854
00:37:05,574 --> 00:37:08,809
谢谢 不过不是因为这个
Thanks, but it's not about that.

855
00:37:08,877 --> 00:37:10,677
好吧
Okay.

856
00:37:10,746 --> 00:37:13,046
我们得信任彼此 Nick
We have to trust each other, Nick,

857
00:37:13,115 --> 00:37:15,849
无论大事还是小事
for the big things and the small things.

858
00:37:15,918 --> 00:37:17,484
这非常重要
It matters.

859
00:37:17,553 --> 00:37:20,187
我犯了个错误 我不该发那条消息
It was a mistake. I shouldn't have sent that text.

860
00:37:20,255 --> 00:37:21,488
那你为什么要发
So why did you?

861
00:37:25,594 --> 00:37:28,862
好吧 晚安 Nick
Okay. Good night, Nick.

862
00:37:30,499 --> 00:37:32,499
Ellie 等等
Ellie, wait.

863
00:37:40,175 --> 00:37:42,676
晚安
Good night.

864
00:37:56,525 --> 00:37:57,724
Kasie 嘿
Kasie, hey.

865
00:37:57,793 --> 00:37:59,926
你 呃 看看这儿有没有想要的东西
Did you, uh, get anything you wanted from here?

866
00:37:59,995 --> 00:38:01,394
这些我不是都需要
'Cause I don't need all this stuff.

867
00:38:01,463 --> 00:38:03,396
噢 没事 我真正想要的
Oh, I'm good. What I really want

868
00:38:03,465 --> 00:38:04,965
是一个他们的数码钟
is one of their Nixie tube clocks.

869
00:38:05,033 --> 00:38:07,467
-噢 那些酷毙了 -我就说嘛 对吧
