870
00:38:07,536 --> 00:38:10,036
我甚至还联系那个公司 问他们能不能
I even called the company to see what it would take

871
00:38:10,105 --> 00:38:11,738
像你的那样 免费送我一个
to send me one for free, like you.

872
00:38:11,807 --> 00:38:13,807
真的吗
Really?

