00:38:13,876 --> 00:38:15,286
真的 我提出可以测试他们所有的产品
Yeah, I offered to test all their products

874
00:38:15,310 --> 00:38:17,210
指出缺陷和种种东西
and point out bugs and stuff,

875
00:38:17,279 --> 00:38:20,814
但他们说 他们从来不赠送免费的礼物
but they said they don't send free gift boxes, ever.

876
00:38:20,883 --> 00:38:22,415
他们说 他们只把东西送给
They said they only send goodies

877
